Color Doc

Package Name:
fifthtry.github.io/color-doc

Color Doc is a color schemes which can be used to change color scheme of web packages via using FTD lang.

To use color-doc color scheme on your web package, add below into FPM.ftd file:

-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/color-doc as colors

-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/color-doc as colors
Import colors into FPM/config.ftd file.
-- import: colors

-- import: colors
